== Umugambi ==
Filime itangirana na Clifford ( Joseph Benjamin ) na Rebecca ( Yvonne Okoro ) bazimiye mu ishyamba nyuma yuko imodoka yabo isabye gusanwa. Byagaragaye ko Rebecca yasezeranijwe na Clifford kuva mu bwana bwabo ko bazabana. Mu gihe Rebecca yacecetse mu rugendo rwose kandi asa nkaho atababajwe n'amagambo yavuzwe n'umugabo we mushya, Clifford agaragaza ko adashaka gushyingiranwa nawe neza kuko yashakaga gusohoza icyifuzo cye cyo gupfa kwa se. Clifford yarumwe nikiremwa cyomwishyamba kandi ibi biganisha kubiganiro byambere hagati yabo. Rebecca amufasha gukira igikomere cye. Aramuhishurira kandi ko mbere yakundaga kandi akagaragaza ko atamwitayeho kubera ko atamwubaha kandi ko amukunda. Nyuma y'ibiganiro birebire hagati yabo, batangiye gukundana. Rebecca ashimuswe nabagabo babiri, nyuma byaje kugaragara ko byateguwe  nuwahoze ari umukunzi we. Rebecca asubira kwa Clifford maze asobanura imigambi ye yose yo guhimbira urupfu rwe no guhagarika umushoferi we kumukurikira amuroga. Nyuma yo kumva no kubona ukuri kwinginga kwe, Clifford aramwakira mugihe bombi bategereje itsinda ryabatabazi.
